    <summary>A Free and Simple to use E-Juice calculator.</summary>
    <description>
        <p>
            E-Juice-Calc is a free and simple to use E-Juice calculator made with Haskell and QML.
            You can calculate the required E-Liquid amounts (VG/PG) with or without the nicotine content and add flavors to your mix. 
            It also supports saving and loading profiles.
        </p>
    </description>
